{"tid":900371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[識真post 加 學術post] 我知點解 Yeonwoo妍雨❤ 靚過 子瑜","createTime":"2018-11-13T07:35:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T11:24:22.000Z","uid":171598,"like":18,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b8ed6c9e0b44a82db1bba5ef1d65b73cbf6027","tid":900371,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T07:35:37.000Z","msg":"因為Yeonwoo妍雨隻眼勁 水潤<br />\n<br />\n以打燈學黎講 <br />\n眼反射到最多光為最靚<br />\n<br />\n所以點解 <br />\n眼比較圓(眼面) <br />\n眼大<br />\n眼黑多白少啲人靚啲 加水潤更靚<br />\n(當然最後到要睇整體五官)<br />\n<br />\n所以打燈時<br />\n一燈左+一白板右<br />\n(如有頂燈 多數有反射到地板光)<br />\n隻眼就有3點<br />\n個時就好靚<br />\n<br />\n(自然光最靚)<br />\n第一張 太陽係頂後少少 眼中光都係黎自環境 妍雨隻眼反射曬 真係靚撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">妍雨</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3nnkaoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3nnkaoO.jpg&h=89c85c49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tNcLXC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tNcLXC.jpg&h=fafcdd8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ca7DGwb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCa7DGwb.jpg&h=c749c5cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">子瑜</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n子瑜隻眼冇咁長 <br />\n偏圓<br />\n都冇咁水潤<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNNXcE7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNNXcE7.jpg&h=2326a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMyzeTt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMyzeTt.jpg&h=f9fe00ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Dckav9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Dckav9.jpg&h=1574d8e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNwUeXQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNwUeXQ.jpg&h=72ccba6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vjRH8hR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvjRH8hR.jpg&h=44e8d9a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我要講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我愛❤Yeonwoo妍雨</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50dc2d6a8f490b2b8417cc78ed4b7c9c4c1fbe9","tid":900371,"uid":89931,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"子瑜&gt;momoland<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c9c492a215747a4e04da722b2b62e5640b8953","tid":900371,"uid":171598,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d50dc2d6a8f490b2b8417cc78ed4b7c9c4c1fbe9","tid":900371,"uid":89931,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T07:39:44.000Z","msg":"子瑜